Privacy Policy

MathTricks - Educational math and science app

Privacy Policy (English)

Last Updated: February 11, 2026

1. Introduction

Welcome to MathTricks, an educational mobile app designed to improve mental math skills and explore math and physics concepts. This policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, and your rights.

2. Data We Collect

  • Usage & analytics: app events and general usage metrics (e.g., Firebase Analytics).
  • Device information: device type, OS version, language, and app version.
  • Advertising data: ad performance and the advertising ID (when required by the platform).
  • Network data: when online features are used (e.g., downloads, assets, or updates).

MathTricks can be used offline for most content, but some features require an internet connection.

3. How We Use Data

  • Improve app quality, content, and performance.
  • Measure audience and app stability.
  • Display and optimize ads where applicable.

4. Third-Party Services

We use trusted services that may process data under their own policies:

  • Google Firebase (Analytics, Storage)
  • Google Mobile Ads (AdMob)

5. Data Sharing

We do not sell personal data. Data may be shared with service providers only to operate the app, comply with legal obligations, or protect users and the service.

6. Childrens Privacy

MathTricks is not specifically directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. Parents can contact us to request deletion.

7. Data Retention & Security

Data is retained only as long as necessary for the purposes described. We apply standard security measures to protect data, including access controls and regular updates.

8. Your Rights

You can request access or deletion of data by contacting us. We will respond as required by applicable law.

9. Changes to This Policy

We may update this policy from time to time. Updates will be published with a new date.

10. Contact

Email: nemesisgalaxie@proton.me

Poltica de Privacidad (Espaol)

Bienvenido a MathTricks, una app educativa para mejorar el clculo mental y explorar conceptos de matemticas y fsica. Esta poltica explica qu datos recopilamos, cmo los usamos y tus derechos.

Politique de Confidentialit (Franais)

Dernire mise jour : 11 fvrier 2026

1. Introduction

Bienvenue sur MathTricks, une application ducative pour amliorer le calcul mental et explorer des notions de mathmatiques et de physique. Cette politique explique les donnes collectes, leur usage et vos droits.

2. Donnes collectes

  • Utilisation & analytics : vnements et mesures d'usage (ex: Firebase Analytics).
  • Informations appareil : type d'appareil, version OS, langue, version de l'app.
  • Donnes publicitaires : performance des pubs et identifiant publicitaire si requis.
  • Donnes rseau : lors de fonctions en ligne (tlchargements, ressources, mises jour).

MathTricks fonctionne majoritairement hors ligne, mais certaines fonctionnalits ncessitent Internet.

3. Utilisation des donnes

  • Amliorer la qualit, le contenu et les performances.
  • Mesurer l'audience et la stabilit.
  • Afficher et optimiser la publicit si applicable.

4. Services tiers

  • Google Firebase (Analytics, Storage)
  • Google Mobile Ads (AdMob)

5. Partage des donnes

Nous ne vendons pas de donnes personnelles. Les donnes peuvent tre partages avec des prestataires pour faire fonctionner l'app, respecter la loi ou proteger les utilisateurs.

6. Donnees des enfants

L'app n'est pas specialement destinee aux moins de 13 ans. Nous ne collectons pas intentionnellement de donnees personnelles. Les parents peuvent demander la suppression des donnees.

7. Conservation et securite

Les donnees sont conservees uniquement le temps necessaire. Nous appliquons des mesures de securite standard.

8. Vos droits

Vous pouvez demander l'acces ou la suppression des donnees en nous contactant.

9. Modifications

Cette politique peut etre mise a jour. La date de mise a jour sera publiee.

10. Contact

Email : nemesisgalaxie@proton.me
